            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximo</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>pro <expan><abbr>salut</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> do<lb break="no" n="3"/><expan><abbr>minor</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratorum</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Octavius <lb n="5"/>Severus |(centurio) <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> VIII <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>praeposit</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>Brit</abbr><ex>tonum</ex></expan> et <expan><abbr>expl</abbr><ex>oratorum</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Auf den Nebenseiten im Relief: links eine Kanne und eine gestielte Opferschale, rechts ein Blitzstrahl. Autopsie R. Wiegels; Hauptbearbeiterin: B. Esch. (B): Schmidt Heidenereich: Z. 2/3: dd/ominor(um).</p>
